					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">When I want to see what's going on at a certain location I use writes to the end of zero page (which is usually free), like "sta $ff" or "sta $fe" and set up breakpoints for the location(s) in question. The writes are meaningless, but they will trigger the breakpoints and I'll be able to trace carefully what happens next.</div>

