					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I find that using something like "STA $5000" works because even when executed, nothing meaningful happens (perhaps if you're using MMC5 it will but I don't know much about that). Also STA "$4500" might work. And since those address ranges aren't used, if I want only some breakpoints to happen, I usually do "STA $5000" in one place, then "STA $5001" in another, "STA $5002" in another, etc.</div>

